Engilbjort!

00:16:23.399 --> 00:16:25.943
Engilbjort!

00:16:26.026 --> 00:16:29.613
-Por que nos incluiu?
-Desculpe.

00:16:29.697 --> 00:16:31.949
Devemos trabalhar juntos.

00:16:32.324 --> 00:16:36.328
